beer.beer_description: Dusk Till Dawn is a doozy, an absolute beauty in fact. We've taken a deep, dark and smooth stout and blended through a significant amount of raspberry. And holy wow, we've got ourselves a decadent raspberry brownie in liquid form. Loads of raspberry on the nose with a smooth, chocolatey base to ooze in on. Perfectly balanced between rich roasty stout and sweet juicy raspberry.
